The David Shayler Radio Show (M4A+MP3 Archive) 11.08.2006 - 03.11.2006 (CD-ROM)

David Shayler Ex-MI5 officer and whistleblower is hosting a new one-hour chat show in the UK on Resonance104.4fm between 8-9pm (GMT) on Friday evenings. The show can also be found on the internet... Find listings for Resonance104.4fm.

Listen to David Shayler talk about his court case against the UK Government, the 7-7 attacks, 9-11, the Iraq war and chemical weapons, false flag terror attacks, Zionism and their plan, Israel, Freemasons and interviews people at the Big Green Gathering Festival, and other events where 9/11 films are being shown to the UK public.

